{"tid":196778,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[女學生衝燈]其實個司機唔一定好大獲","createTime":"2017-04-11T13:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T14:24:25.000Z","uid":10843,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"70f308781c0dcb9a37817a2b713393b9d0f196ff","tid":196778,"uid":10843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T13:50:22.000Z","msg":"有好多人覺得個司機而家比人告危險駕駛引致他人死亡一定要坐幾碌走唔甩<br />\n於是我就上網搵下如果司機撞到個唔守交通規則既途人係咪一定係好嚴重呢？<br />\n咁我就搵到呢單新聞(15年6月24日)：<br />\n<br />\n疑貪方便棄交通燈設施 清潔工「黃格仔」過路遭撞斃\t<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】一名與丈夫艱辛工作多年養大子女的婦人，原定明年可退休享福及弄孫為樂，詎料昨晨她上班時疑貪方便，在新蒲崗彩虹道未有用鄰近交通燈過路設施，亂過馬路，遭駛至私家車撞拋10 米外重傷倒地，送院不治。警方列作「致命交通意外」案處理，拘捕涉案司機帶署扣查。<br />\n<br />\n私家車司機涉危駕致死被捕<br />\n<br />\n被捕男司機姓陳，42 歲，涉嫌「危險駕駛引致他人死亡」罪名，被帶署扣查。<br />\n<br />\n女死者姓葉，59 歲，家住彩頤花園，在伊利沙伯醫院任職清潔工10 多年，人稱「卿姐」，工友形容她「好好人，好做得嘢」。<br />\n<br />\n咁我睇返呢單案既判決(無中文，得英文)<br />\nHKSAR v. CHAN YUET KWONG (07/06/2016, DCCC5/2016)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/search/search_result_detail_frame.jsp?DIS=104430&amp;QS=%28%E5%8D%B1%E9%9A%AA%E9%A7%95%E9%A7%9B%E5%BC%95%E8%87%B4%E4%BB%96%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%29&amp;TP=RS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fsearch%2Fsearch_result_detail_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D104430%26QS%3D%2528%25E5%258D%25B1%25E9%259A%25AA%25E9%25A7%2595%25E9%25A7%259B%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%2587%25B4%25E4%25BB%2596%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%2529%26TP%3DRS&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VYsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=58e2e32d\" target=\"_blank\">http://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/search/search_result_detail_frame.jsp?DIS=104430&amp;QS=%28%E5%8D%B1%E9%9A%AA%E9%A7%95%E9%A7%9B%E5%BC%95%E8%87%B4%E4%BB%96%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%29&amp;TP=RS</a><br />\n發現雖然個司機「危險駕駛引致他人死亡」罪成，但都係判200個鐘社會服務令，佢仲要有酒駕前科，同埋發生車禍時無買第三者保險<br />\n<br />\n結論：係呢件事上面有公義，司機只係留左案底同做200個鐘社會服務，所以亦都唔需要針對女學生覺得佢累死個司機"},{"pid":"5b9a056259656908534a2021bc9a80272795fa7f","tid":196778,"uid":15813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T13:52:05.000Z","msg":"心理上同聲譽唔計入影響裡面？<br />\n都仲未計呢排佢一定無工開先"},{"pid":"60cf5632570d717f42b3ccde076b5eb7057aecf7","tid":196778,"uid":52323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T13:55:12.000Z","msg":"收入，陰影呢？"},{"pid":"45e9a9f78c7fc83afbb8b2a13d0eccb188aea29c","tid":196778,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T13:58:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8472d566c8058d5ebb8a82a48d8ed8e81585e44","tid":196778,"uid":52323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:04:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢咁嘅年紀<br />\n案底都影響唔到佢</blockquote><br />\n咁撚仆街嘅野你都講得出嘅"},{"pid":"b92906865721add3d7d963d92b80d26247644505","tid":196778,"uid":41138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:05:23.000Z","msg":"年年都有既事年年都嘈一次 不過今次最精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61fd93553b03167ed6bdcc5395b71a410d4d93c0","tid":196778,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:09:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a5e7603dd9302b29ec4b7df8f50ff2cf50530f7","tid":196778,"uid":103318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:11:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢咁嘅年紀<br />\n案底都影響唔到佢</blockquote><br />\n咁撚仆街嘅野你都講得出嘅</blockquote><br />\n佢係咁㗎啦，又話想完善政策，你全家衝出馬路死撚咗咪有人完善囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0bd5ebf84ac4d30cb7197a323f80472336ba8c","tid":196778,"uid":94568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:12:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢咁嘅年紀<br />\n案底都影響唔到佢</blockquote><br />\n咁撚仆街嘅野你都講得出嘅</blockquote><br />\n班人話個女仔抵死啲說話仲仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8897c10dbb948bd0903cbcd66c5c956ed65c7f9d","tid":196778,"uid":103318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:13:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢咁嘅